WEBVTT

00:03:59.974 --> 00:04:03.284
And two weeks later,
the inspector comes, looks around,

00:04:03.308 --> 00:04:05.973
says, "OK, the concrete
is still wet right over there,

00:04:05.997 --> 00:04:07.849
that part's not quite up to code ...

00:04:08.838 --> 00:04:10.196
I'll give it an 80 percent."

00:04:10.220 --> 00:04:11.284
(Laughter)

00:04:11.308 --> 00:04:14.043
You say, "Great! That's a C.
Let's build the first floor."

00:04:14.067 --> 00:04:15.085
(Laughter)

00:04:15.109 --> 00:04:16.263
Same thing.

00:04:16.287 --> 00:04:20.126
We have two weeks, do what you can,
inspector shows up, it's a 75 percent.

00:04:20.150 --> 00:04:21.309
Great, that's a D-plus.

00:04:21.333 --> 00:04:22.579
Second floor, third floor,

00:04:22.603 --> 00:04:25.381
and all of a sudden,
while you're building the third floor,

00:04:25.405 --> 00:04:26.841
the whole structure collapses.

00:04:26.865 --> 00:04:30.109
And if your reaction is the reaction
you typically have in education,